{"tid":1395061,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日我同一個新移民的對話","createTime":"2019-08-01T15:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T02:23:48.000Z","uid":252178,"like":70,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"744a537ed7d2e0d8c1e353ed243cba0e50c4ee07","tid":1395061,"uid":252178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:36:45.000Z","msg":"今日我同一個新移民傾左好耐計<br />\n發覺其實新移民嘅人諗野未必係極藍<br />\n佢地某部份人大多都係一無所知 人云亦云<br />\n而我發覺佢心地唔差 所以我同佢展開左一輪理性的對話<br />\n各位如果遇上不太激進的港豬或大陸人 都可以參考下<br />\n呢班新移民又趕唔到佢地走 隨時可能係其中一個選民<br />\n不如溫柔咁感化佢地（只限於善良的新移民）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=新移民<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：上次我見到有個後生同全家人鬧大交，原因係家人唔比佢出去遊行，唉....<span style=\"color: red;\">點解唔肯聽下大人講野</span>呢？為左咁小事同屋企人鬧交<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：其實可能個後生有佢嘅原因，個大人有無聽佢解釋？可能當時大家都好激動，但如果比著係你，咩都無問，一來就話你收左錢或比人煽動，貶低你有個人思考，你嬲唔嬲？佢地唔係小學生，有自己思考㗎啦喎<br />\n如果個家長有細心聆聽仔女的原因，而仔女有平靜地解釋原因，可能就會好啲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：但我聽人講佢地真係<span style=\"color: red;\">收左錢</span>，可能只係少數人無收錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：至少我話比你知我無收錢，如果我比三千蚊你比人打穿頭你願意嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁都係...<span style=\"color: red;\">但都唔好搞到我</span>，上次我幫呀女去入境處搞證件，好驚有人搞事要再預約呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔怕，好多時呢啲都會事先通知㗎，唔會咁突然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<span style=\"color: red;\">有事先通知就好啦</span>，咁我可以預早少少去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<span style=\"color: red;\">啲後生唔驚出解放軍㗎咩</span>？如果好似六四咁咁亂我唔想呀 嗰啲乜野王丹申請到庇護就話啫 你地申請唔到咁點算<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：放心啦出解放軍時啲商家驚過你呀，到時樓價大跌，大量撤資，而香港係資本主義社會，政府聽有錢佬話，加上大陸其實都要靠香港，點會咁易出解放軍 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：原來關資本主義事，哈哈，樓價跌就好囉<br />\n我啲朋友呀話<span style=\"color: red;\">上海深圳一早超越左香港</span>啦，點會靠香港呀？好多人都去上海深圳投資<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：如果香港咁差就唔會每年咁多大陸人落黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：吖都係呀，我都係因為覺得香港好落黎，我覺得香港政府唔應該比咁多人落黎啦，多到無地方住<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係㗎 香港根本唔係因為無地 係因為太多人 日日放咁多人落黎多多地都唔夠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你知唔知咩係社會信用評級，你知唔知大陸好多地方實行緊？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔知呀，咩黎㗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：一個系統你做左啲咩都會評分，亂拋垃圾、亂過馬路又扣分，可能扣到你無得搭火車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁其實個系統都幾好吖，中國人咁多人係要管下，但係我啲同鄉成日都亂拋垃圾，我都成日亂過馬路，咁我一定好低分啦哈哈哈<br />\n雖然個系統幾好，但好似太嚴囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：香港第日可能會實行，你覺得點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：好似唔係咁好囉....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我八月五號搭高鐵返鄉下，唔知會唔會有影響呢？啲人罷工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔會搞高鐵啦，不過多謝你間接支持左罷工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：其實政治嘅野我咩都唔識㗎哈哈哈，只要唔好搞到我就得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：有時政治嘅野你唔搞佢，佢都會隨時搞到你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：其實係咪政府一日唔回應件事都唔會結束？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係㗎 所以如果你想社會快啲回復正常應該問政府<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁政府真係唔係好得喎....<br />\n<br />\n另外我解釋左好多咩係送中條例，點解啲人要反<br />\n同埋點解元朗件事啲人咁嬲<br />\n佢連當年佔中發生咩事佢都唔知 但佢落左黎香港已經超過十年<br />\n其實好多人對場運動都一知半解，如果身邊的人係好港豬的話，不防先冷靜解釋，好過一黎就同佢嘈/ unfriend左佢"},{"pid":"8d11dd076731f79ada5699525acc89e74d083520","tid":1395061,"uid":252178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:39:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69688f84a97f49b3d6be97d76bcc9087cf7fa24d","tid":1395061,"uid":175722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:42:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"76045f721c023d05f9ac53019a108500e363e67f","tid":1395061,"uid":252178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:52:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"82c8537227a1f465b6a096fd0e36c303564c7ad6","tid":1395061,"uid":252178,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:03:35.000Z","msg":"我地要connect唔同嘅人<br />\n無論佢地不同背景<br />\n只要佢地係善良的 都可以感化到"},{"pid":"7e70a9cf6282021c8bbaeeeab4882380d3f81f4a","tid":1395061,"uid":188959,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"佢肯聽你講已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cbf6e102ff8854fdc4c3f623c3320ead8de02e","tid":1395061,"uid":252178,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"7e70a9cf6282021c8bbaeeeab4882380d3f81f4a","tid":1395061,"uid":188959,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"佢肯聽你講已經好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:13:56.000Z","msg":"對住政治冷感的人 首先要講啲佢覺得切身嘅野先<br />\n同埋啲用語不能太難明<br />\n要一聽落去關佢事<br />\n同埋唔好有種令佢覺得你苛責佢嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16941bf1b3ef4ec2b491c97af955a71288acf581","tid":1395061,"uid":252178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:21:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c5b77b2247886bfaef67bc968824e52a0b922d3","tid":1395061,"uid":252178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f49e5bbb4334503ac9a0164a723ad451ef50429","tid":1395061,"uid":184928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:46:17.000Z","msg":"你都話有得對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同新移民同事講起政治話題<br />\n佢就一味話啲人收錢做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想同佢嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />影響關係"},{"pid":"d178be3a2df68633c3b3f31142dbdfa5fc89c4a7","tid":1395061,"uid":252178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f49e5bbb4334503ac9a0164a723ad451ef50429","tid":1395061,"uid":184928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:46:17.000Z","msg":"你都話有得對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同新移民同事講起政治話題<br />\n佢就一味話啲人收錢做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想同佢嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />影響關係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:52:19.000Z","msg":"試下問佢 比錢佢肯唔肯上前線？<br />\n因為佢地啲乜wechat gp太多呢類資訊<br />\n佢地有時唔係心地唔好<br />\n係比人洗腦 慢慢導返條正軌比佢地"},{"pid":"ad0f9a247309467ef7eb44fdf3325aae62469f96","tid":1395061,"uid":295803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6f49e5bbb4334503ac9a0164a723ad451ef50429","tid":1395061,"uid":184928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:46:17.000Z","msg":"你都話有得對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同新移民同事講起政治話題<br />\n佢就一味話啲人收錢做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想同佢嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji